=== Noun ===
'''fire hydrant'''

#A device used by [[firefighter]]s to obtain water from the main. It consists of a barrel, connections for hose and a valve assembly. There are two common types, wet barrel and dry barrel. Hydrants designed to reduce water theft are called [[custodial hydrants]]


